Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.14,0:01:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概快了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个国家应该有修车行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度表一直坏着 感觉很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 这不会影响你的行驶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.12,0:01:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着要前往的 似乎是个科学技术相当发达的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.82,0:01:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度表这种小问题 一定能轻易地修好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.82,0:01:59.25,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}速度表：Speed Meter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外我的悬吊系统也不太正常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:01.83,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}悬吊系统（Suspension）：由车身与轮胎间的弹簧与避震器组成整个支持系统。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.13,0:02:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转向系统、轮毂轴承也开始松动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.13,0:02:05.29,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}转向系统：Steering System；轮毂轴承：Wheel Bearing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员太粗暴的话 摩托车可是很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这一带
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往前一点看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.55,0:02:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.36,0:02:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.86,0:02:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没料到这边会有人出现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到在这个森林中能遇见外人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是人而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫奇诺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的同伴 艾尔梅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟能和其它机械同伴说话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺你们要去哪里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近有没有一个国家？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想要去那个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就是找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这附近没有国家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺 艾尔梅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去使用我的宅邸呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用你？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是那间宅邸的女佣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:24.24,标题1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,250)\fad(500,100)}机械人偶的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里最适合幸福的家庭居住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷他们马上就会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关奇诺你们的事 到时我会拜托老爷的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我去收衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺你们请在那边的房间稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的房间？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是右边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左边啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧 猜错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不一定是猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许她是要我们在这下面等她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是死不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我擅自进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我的制造者的研究室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我的制造者」？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是机械人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械人偶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了照顾居住在此的老爷、夫人和少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而被制造出来的机械人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我这老机械人所做的菜能合您的口味 那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是旅行者奇诺和摩托车艾尔梅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺 艾尔梅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是老爷、夫人和少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从婆婆那听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到隔壁去补充能源了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行者 来 请别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以请问一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于那位老婆婆的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她本人自称是机械人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您听说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她工作很勤奋 帮了我们很大的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了她 我们夫妻才能一起出外工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都在工作吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在食品公司 内人则是在国家的区公所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儿子在上幼年学校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以再请问您一件事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近有没有一个国家？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近没有国家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想旅行者你走错路了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这附近是片深邃的森林呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会走错也难怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 各位是到哪里去工作呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这附近没有国家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你是走错路了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这附近是片很深的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会走错也难怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 小弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的晚餐觉得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡肉真是煮得太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙款待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的工作呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺 合您的口味吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃的都忘神了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 还真是吓了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们不吃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想抢来吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为有那样与人类完全相像的机械人偶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了地下室的装备后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会让人信以为真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家族感觉也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像在看一出没有感情的戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 今天先睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没睡床了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 各位时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 路上请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟出门去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有合您的口味吗？奇诺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我最近吃的早餐中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无庸置疑最美味的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 我有件事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造你的人究竟是谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有被输入这个情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所知的仅是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋子的打扫方式 煮菜的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有哄少爷入睡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 奇诺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午我带您去一个很棒的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您瞧瞧一个很稀奇的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要让我们看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是古代冰河凿出的峡谷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多能看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您仔细观察峡谷深处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是国家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是太古的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是由于某个可怜的原因才会毁灭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在这个季节的这个时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因光线的增减 使湖水变得澄澈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此看上去才会如此湛蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您觉得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定曾有很多人住在那儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相扶助着生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你已经发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个国家…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说那个国家的遗迹仍相当的新
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么看 都不是太古的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在找的国家 说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 或许根本就是那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 告诉我们的是个老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定不知道那个国家毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 那老婆婆不知道也太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她看起来也不像在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之已经发现目的地了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点我已经想过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们再待一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 那是因为我个人的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 修理完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「好 修理完成」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 仪表还是坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我修不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得去钟表行才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 暂时先不管了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我查看一下那个故障吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:12:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样应该行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒 好棒 简直太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆 真的很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是机械人偶 这种事不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮上别人 我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是机油有点不够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我太老旧 到处都有问题出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在老爷们回来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得准备好晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆的身体好像还是不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她工作得很勤奋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不眠不休地工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许她真的是机械呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆看着那家人时的眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼神怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.09,0:14:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械的寿命…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来到我坏掉的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去和大家道别
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您带我去见他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在的状况实在不宜上楼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫大家来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有帮上大家的忙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是她的丈夫跟儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢让我们在此留宿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺你不想知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「刚才埋葬的人究竟是谁？」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我们三人又是什么人？」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「沉于湖水深处的又是什么国家？」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我洗耳恭听
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请你先看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个谷底深处的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从建国以来就有两个民族互相憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断地发生争执
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在五十几年前 是那个国家的机械工学博士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时她才三十岁出头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为这个世界屈指可数的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她才能修好速度表啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她厌倦了国家的研究设施
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将自己的家改建成研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的目标是制作机械人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她如此设想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械人偶能将全人类从劳动中解放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个结果将导致人们更有空闲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以停止人们互相憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她专心致力于研究中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日复一日 每天都在研究室度过数个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其心爱的先生和可爱的孩子相处的时间相当地短暂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直都注视着她的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后她终于成功地使三台机械人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有了完美的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些机械人偶就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们三人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直等待着 在完成我们时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向其所爱的两人宣告此项研究的成功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她准备了小小的宴会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因民族纷争而生的恐怖炸弹袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瓦砾堆中发现丈夫与儿子尸体的她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回首说道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「好了 大家 我们来庆祝吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后 她也随即被压在瓦砾堆下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把她救了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地下研究室中治疗她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数日后 她恢复了意识
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已不再是制造我们那时的她了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒来的她对我们如此说道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你们是我工作场所的家人吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以为自己是机械人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后怎样了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们等待她身体恢复的期间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国内的憎恨越发激烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…最终使用了强力的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为了不使她回忆起悲伤的过往
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因而建了水坝 将国家沉于湖底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在森林中完美地再现她曾经过着幸福日子时的公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在之后的54年341天中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们扮演了她所渴望的幸福的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也知道她的身体变弱了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只有衰老是我们束手无策的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们说的有趣的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要走了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要直接出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是奇诺小姐走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我们要做什么才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要你们自己决定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为帮助人类而被制作出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不替人类做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将毫无存在的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事是我们可以帮奇诺去做的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以成为你所需要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以成为你的朋友、父母
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以成为你的孩子、情人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以成为你的仆人、敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类不是要与某人一同生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是要替某人活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则不是会很痛苦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这因人而异
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们帮不上你的忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.24,0:22:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.17,0:22:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:23:51.02,NEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.17,0:23:54.87,预告标题,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「她的旅行」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.09,0:23:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行时最需要注意的事是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.49,0:24:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,譬如购物时要小心别受骗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.22,0:24:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留心携带的食粮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.26,0:24:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意旅行的必需品
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.19,0:24:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时还要注意还价
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.93,0:24:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐变得琐碎了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.35,0:24:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 最需要小心的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.17,0:24:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.25,0:00:10.78,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}空は果てしない 心の鏡だからね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:20.04,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}毎日色を変えてく 映し出すように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:28.07,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}白く はいた 煙 雲になって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:32.77,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}こぼれ そうな 涙 隠していて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:37.39,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}信じる 物が 壊れてく時には
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:40.93,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}目を閉じて願う
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:50.47,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}一人きりで 眠れない 夜に落ちても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:01:04.68,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}闇の中に 瞳とじて 星の輝きに耳を澄ましてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.93,0:01:13.96,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}譲れないから 裸足でも 走り続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:28.44,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}蒼い空の 月のように 儚さ抱いて手を伸ばしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.25,0:00:10.78,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}天空广阔无垠 只因那是心之明镜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:20.04,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}每日都映照出与昔迥异的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:28.07,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}喷吐的白烟 化作云朵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:32.77,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}滑落的泪水 悄悄隐藏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:37.39,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}坚信的事物 崩溃之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:40.93,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}轻闭双眼 默默乞愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:50.47,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}就算独自身临难以入眠的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:01:04.68,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}亦可于黑暗中阖上双眸 侧耳倾听群星的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.93,0:01:13.96,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}因为绝不退让 即便一无所有 也要继续前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:28.44,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}想要伸手怀抱青空中 那宛若月亮般的虚幻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:51.30,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}遠くで降りだした雨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.77,0:23:02.26,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}だれかが濡れながら そっと震える
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:07.48,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}森に迷い 空に寄り添う
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.18,0:23:12.66,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}国を訪ね 人と行き交い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:21.23,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,400)}そして旅は終わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.35,0:23:27.49,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}So the Beautiful World
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:34.24,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}何処から来た 何処まで行く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:38.19,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)}So the Beautiful World
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.37,0:23:47.65,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,400)}流れるまま 世界を走る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:51.30,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}远方雨点洒落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.77,0:23:02.26,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}是谁淋着雨 悄悄颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:07.48,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}迷失森林 靠近天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.18,0:23:12.66,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}寻访各色国度 与人交错相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:21.23,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,400)}旅途将永无止境
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.35,0:23:27.49,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}So the Beautiful World
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:34.24,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}从何而来 又将从何而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:38.19,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}So the Beautiful World
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.37,0:23:47.65,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,400)}任之漂流 走遍世界
